{"type":null,"faqId":37064,"title":"手环可以连接几部手机？是否可以是同系统(同为安卓系统或IOS系统)的手机","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>手环支持连接两部手机，手环可接听两部手机的来电。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>一个手环可以同时连接两部手机，用来接通电话，消息推送等。但是手环蓝牙连接两个同系统(同为安卓系统或IOS系统)的手机，相同系统数据通道只有1个，因此不能同时同步数据，但一个安卓和一个IOS是可以的。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2228","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1440750141000,"seriesProductName":"B2","visitedTimes":148,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"华为手环,B2,连接两部手机,更换手机连接,数据同步,同系统连接","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}